# Copy to .dev.vars for local `wrangler dev` testing (gitignored).
# In production this is set with: wrangler secret put GITHUB_TOKEN
#
# Fine-grained, READ-ONLY, single-repo (arnislvdev/monarch) GitHub PAT.
# Scope: Contents: read-only. Nothing else. See main monarch repo's
# .env.example for the same pattern used by the app's in-app updater.
GITHUB_TOKEN=
